children.text: Wyndham Santa Monica - At The Pier

120 Colorado Ave
Santa Monica, CA 90401, US
Add a photo or text description

So convenient! For someone who didn't know the area and had limited time to start with, it was great knowing where I was going to park and knowing that I was able to leave my car in a safe, convenient location. Great service!! Thank you!

Let's face it, Santa Monica can be a nightmare to park, and pricey, to boot. You either know SM, and where to park, or you don't. Visitors like me just don't. (And the City of SM has made a parking enforcement a profit center, so the ticket-writers are always cruising like sharks.) Parkme's reservation and pre-paid system took all the unknowns out of my business appointment in SM. The folks at the Wyndham (spelling?) were professional, friendly and excellent in every way. This is an excellent service, all the way around. I've bookmarked it.

(Jenson) deserves special recognition.  He tended to us both times on our trip.  This young man made certain we were cared for.  As an older woman on a long road trip I appreciated he made certain we didn't have any issues assessing the restricted bathroom quickly.  We were able to refresh ourselves in the lobby, enjoy the pier and a restaurant for a while, then head back on the road.   I was much more alert to tackle that traffic again toward our destinations. While not required, I left a tip for Jenson for his attention to customer service.   Westlake Village Inn could have used people like him (hint).
